cinvestav.android.pki.cryptography.cert
Class X509CRLRevokedCertificateEntry

java.lang.Object
  cinvestav.android.pki.cryptography.cert.X509CRLRevokedCertificateEntry

public class X509CRLRevokedCertificateEntry
extends java.lang.Object

This class contains all the elements required by a x509 CRL in order to add an entry for a revoked certificate, includes, the certificate to be revoked, the reason, date and some other extensions
